name: InteractWith
description: What is the project about? InteractWith - NFTs infrastructure for apps (APIs, SDKs, Dashboard, Wallet) a combination of MetaMask, Twitter and Stripe. Plug-and-play integration tools for developers to build on blockchain. Integrate NFTs into any app with only a few lines of code. NFT onramp infrastructure for Fiat to Crypto - Building a familiar web2 user experience by selling NFTs via credit cards. What makes your project unique? Our dedication to accelerate the adoption of blockchain technology by bringing compelling mass-market web3 integration tools. History of your project.
